{"tid":2436411,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"半百居英港人集會打氣","createTime":"2021-03-07T06:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T06:35:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7c86531565159ce990cd99948ba19d54045b13ee","tid":2436411,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:28:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210307/BJSFP4KEBNDI3JUGMF6X6PE5ME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210307%2FBJSFP4KEBNDI3JUGMF6X6PE5ME%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bJIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=3c38f2c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210307%2FBJSFP4KEBNDI3JUGMF6X6PE5ME%2F&h=a3867312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210307/BJSFP4KEBNDI3JUGMF6X6PE5ME/</a><br />\n<br />\n半百居英港人集會打氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8q9glHYlqFg68_wwqHBXJ5vgt7Y=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QN72E2NCARDYNHK3ELAAL7OSVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8q9glHYlqFg68_wwqHBXJ5vgt7Y%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQN72E2NCARDYNHK3ELAAL7OSVU.jpg&h=dc566cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■英國諾定咸昨午有港人發起集會聲援47人，有父母攜同孩子出席。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】英國各地均有人發起聲援香港47人行動，繼日前的倫敦、曼徹斯特和雷丁三城，昨日中午在諾定咸（Nottingham）市中心亦有港人發起集會，近50人出席，歷時近一小時，有父母帶同小孩參與，亦有英國人出席，以向香港傳遞來自英國的聲援及關注。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：官拒批暫時保釋 11人續還柙  孕妻舉BB超聲波照  隔犯人欄為張可森打氣<br />\n<br />\n集會在Brian Clough Statue前舉行，因疫情關係參與者全隔開近兩米隔離站立，除「光時」旗外，亦舉起各式各樣手寫的標語，包括「Release All Political Prisoners」、「Democracy is not a crime」、「Free Hong Kong」等，集會亦有播放《願榮光歸香港》，眾人偶然高喊「光復香港 時代革命」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n看新聞落淚<br />\n<br />\n活動發起人之一Sally（化名）表示，舉辦集會除了希望聲援47人外，由於諾定咸有越來越多港人移民，希望能夠透過集會把身在此城的港人聚集起來。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：寫信聲援 市民︰佢哋幫60萬人頂<br />\n<br />\n區太及丈夫帶同兒子出席集會，區太表示，作為香港人即使去到世界各地亦應。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者李雨夢英國報道"},{"pid":"7e373e0efa5bc9e02ac856dfab8e8f4b44e1504e","tid":2436411,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:31:15.000Z","msg":"英國疫情數字回落得好快<br />\n遲D相信會越來越多人過來呢邊<br />\n越來越多人企出來"},{"pid":"44bfb9ef0aa2608b655917092d33d88344ab867c","tid":2436411,"uid":166506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33abe3a072c9a183205074b8c86985c684fa27a3","tid":2436411,"uid":132810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e373e0efa5bc9e02ac856dfab8e8f4b44e1504e","tid":2436411,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:31:15.000Z","msg":"英國疫情數字回落得好快<br />\n遲D相信會越來越多人過來呢邊<br />\n越來越多人企出來"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T06:35:09.000Z","msg":"我都想移"}]}